INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('3551','571','0','ECS003551','佳能600D(18-55)','+','143','0','','100','0.000','4200.00','3500.00','0.00','0','0','1','600D 入门单反','','<h1 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: bold 26px/34px 微软雅黑; text-transform: none; color: rgb(34,34,34); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); text-align: center; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">出色入门单反 佳能 600D套机特价3500</h1>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br clear=\"all\" style=\"font-size: 0px; line-height: 0\" />\r\n<img id=\"content-first-img\" alt=\"翻转屏幕、高清摄像 佳能600D套机5450元 \" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/114/606/ceS1ugzSo7wxk.jpg\" style=\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n图为：佳能单反<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera_index/subcate15_list_1.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">相机</a>E0S&nbsp;<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera/index231069.shtml\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">600D</a></p>\r\n<p sizset=\"false\" sizcache=\"4\" sizcache0825952908835589=\"4 11 174\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 整体来说，佳能 600D的外观与550D没有太大的差别，该机采用塑料材质机身，增加了表面蒙皮的面积，防滑性能有所提升，并且有效的提升了视觉感受，显得更有档次。<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera/index231069.shtml\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">佳能600D</a>的机身净重510g，装上电池及存储卡后的重量为570g，相当于一个满罐可乐加一个2/3罐可乐的重量。在机身色彩方面，佳能600D依然只为用户提供了传统而经典的纯黑色机身。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" sizset=\"false\" sizcache=\"2\" sizcache0825952908835589=\"4 11 177\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 佳能600D采用了一块3英寸104万像素高清晰可旋转液晶屏，配置与佳能中端单反<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://detail.zol.com.cn/digital_camera/index231067.shtml\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">60D</a>完全相同。该屏幕显示效果处于目前所有<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://dcdv.zol.com.cn/dslr.html\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">单反相机</a>的顶级水平，可自由旋转的设计也使得取景方便很多。从目前单反<a class=\"hui14_line\" href=\"http://dcdv.zol.com.cn/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0); border-bottom: rgb(255,79,79) 1px dashed\">相机</a>的发展趋势来看，实时取景搭配旋转屏的设计正在逐渐普及。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" sizset=\"false\" sizcache=\"2\" sizcache0825952908835589=\"5 12 3\" jquery1361869508799=\"15\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"翻转LCD+全新套头 佳能入门新贵600D上市 \" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/114/607/ceayLpYV5VC2s.jpg\" style=\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid\" />&nbsp;<img alt=\"翻转LCD+全新套头 佳能入门新贵600D上市 \" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/114/607/ceayLpYV5VC2s.jpg\" style=\"border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid\" /><br />\r\n图为：佳能单反相机E0S 600D</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" sizset=\"175\" sizcache=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 佳能 600D的核心硬件没有太多的升级之处，不过在软件方面却有着不小的升级。在模式转盘上，该机增加了全新的AUTO+场景智能自动模式（即绿色档），将相机调至此模式之后，用户不用再调整任何复杂的参数，只需要按动快门就可以拍摄出效果令人满意的照片，非常智能，很适合初学者使用。</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" sizset=\"false\" sizcache=\"2\" sizcache0825952908835589=\"4 11 179\" style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 14px 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/25px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(245,248,253); orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<table bordercolor=\"#a2c7e1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"4\" width=\"500\" align=\"center\" border=\"1\" sizset=\"false\" sizcache0825952908835589=\"4 11 179\" style=\"clear: right; margin: 0px auto; word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px simsun; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; l