自动适应所连接设备的传输速率、全/半双工模式。</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#0080ff\" size=\"4\">即插即用</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#0080ff\" size=\"4\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.tenda.com.cn/uploadfile/product/TEH1600S/example3.jpg\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; float: right; margin-left: 20px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" /></font>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; line-height: 1.4; padding-top: 0px\"><font color=\"#0080ff\" size=\"4\">TEH1600S的自适应RJ45端口，支持NWAY自动协商(自适应)功能，自动侦测传输速率、双工模式，自动选择一种最佳的网络连接模式，真正做到即插即用。采用存储--转发模式，支持MAC地址自动学习功能，集成4K的MAC地址, 充分满足各种应用的需求。</font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#0080ff\" size=\"4\">设计合理</font></div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">\r\n<p style=\"